  "privacyPolicyTitle": "गोपनीयता Policy",
  "privacyLastUpdated": "Last updated: March 2025",
  "privacyIntro": "At {appName}, your गोपनीयता is paramount. This गोपनीयता Policy explains how we collect, use, store, and protect your personal and health-related data. By using our services, you agree to the practices described below.",
  "privacySectionDataCollection": "1. Data Collection",
  "privacyDataCollectionBody": "We collect the following categories of data: • Personal Information: Nनाम ईमेल address, फ़ोन number, तारीख of birth, and gender. • स्वास्थ्य Data: Blood type, aएलर्जी chronic conditions, mदवाएं vital signs, symptom logs, and ट्रायज results. • आपातकाल Contacts: Names, फ़ोन numbers, and relationships of your designated contacts. • Device Data: Device type, operating system, and app version for compatibility and sसमर्थन • Usage Data: Feature interactions and anonymized analytics to improve our services. We only collect data that is necessary for providing our स्वास्थ्य companion services. You have full control over what information you provide.",
  "privacySectionDataStorage": "2. Data Storage & Encryption",
  "privacyDataStorageBody": "Your data is stored using industry-leading security measures:\n\n• Encryption at Rest: All data stored in our databases is encrypted using AES-256 encryption.\n• Encryption in Transit: All data transmitted between your device and our servers uses TLS 1.3 encryption.\n• Health Passport: Your health passport data is encrypted with a unique key derived from your credentials.\n• QR कोड Sharing: Shared health data via QR codes is encrypted and time-limited.\n• Infrastructure: Our servers are hosted in SOC 2 Type II certified data centers with 24/7 monitoring.\n\nWe do not store payment card information. All payment processing is handled by certified third-party providers.",
  "privacySectionGdpr": "3. GDPR Compliance",
  "privacyGdprBody": "{appName} is fully compliant with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR): • Lawful Basis: We process your data based on your explicit consent and contractual necessity. • Data Minimization: We only collect and process data that is strictly necessary. • Purpose Limitation: Your data is used only for the purposes for which it was collected. • Right to Access: You can request a complete copy of your personal data at any tसमय • Right to Rectification: You can update or correct your data through the app sसेटिंग्स • Right to Erasure: You can request complete deletion of your account and data. • Right to Portability: You can निर्यात your data in a machine-readable format. • Data Processing Agreements: सभी third-party processors have signed DPAs. • Cross-Border Transfers: Data is processed within the EU/EEA unless explicit consent is given otherwise.",
  "privacySectionYourRights": "4. Your Rights",
  "privacyRightsBody": "You have the following rights regarding your data: • Access: View सभी your personal and स्वास्थ्य data within the app or request a data eनिर्यात • Correction: संपादित करें your प्रोफ़ाइल information at any समय through संपादित करें Pप्रोफ़ाइल • Deletion: Request account deletion through सेटिंग्स > Data & गोपनीयता > हटाएं Account. • Restriction: Limit how certain data is processed by adjusting your notification and sharing preferences. • Objection: Object to specific data processing activities by contacting our Data Protection Officer. • Withdrawal of Consent: You may withdraw consent at any समय without affecting the lawfulness of prior processing. To exercise any of these rights, contact us at privacy@vitalseker.com or through the in-app समर्थन feature.",
  "privacySectionContactUs": "5. Contact Us",
  "privacyContactBody": "If you have any questions or concerns बारे में this गोपनीयता Policy or our data practices, please contact us: • Eईमेल privacy@vitalseker.com • Sसमर्थन support@vitalseker.com • Data Protection Officer: dpo@vitalseker.com • Address: {producer}, Data Protection Office We aim to respond to सभी privacy-related inquiries within 30 days.",
